features: *️⃣【Dresser with Column Design】This dressers & chests of drawers is equipped with column design. 3 metal columns are designed in the bedroom dresser, and the clean and streamlined look makes this dressers for bedroom more attractive and unique. And the open storage design also add modern aesthetics to the dresser. Moreover, the high-quality, water-resistant finish can be easily cleaned and maintained.

*️⃣【Multi-Variable RGB Lights】The black dresser features a built-in RGB LED light strip that can display a variety of colors and can be adjustable for brightness. In addition, there are several other lighting modes available to suit different moods and occasions. Moreover, there are a few songs on the app, and the led lights can change color with music rhythm.

*️⃣【Convenient Charging Station】The chest of drawers is arranged with 2 AC and 2 USB socket. One of USB ports is designed for the led lights, the AC socket and the other USB socket provide convenience for charging your phone, earphone, desk lamp, and other small electrical appliances. And the chest of drawers for bedroom is convenient for charging devices in any room, be it in the bedroom or living room.

*️⃣ 【Sufficient Storage Space】The 6 drawer dresser completes with 6 big drawers, and large top surface for additional storage, so lingerie, blankets, underwear as well as clothes of your family members can be stored well. The wood table top and the open storage are designed for simple storage, placing glasses, alarm clocks, table lamps, magazines, books, and even skin care products.

*️⃣【Easy installation and Customer Service】The dresser is made of eco-friendly particle board and metal materials. Comes with detailed instructions and tools, it is recommended to follow the steps in the accompanying instructions, then lay out each board by number, and finally assemble, which will make the installation more easier. Any questions about the led dresser, please feel free to contact us, and we will do our best to solve your problems with 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Fun but be careful putting it together!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I do love this dresser and it was a gamble buying it since there aren't any reviews or there wasn't when I bought it. It has rolling drawers which I love. It has a rave light setting and if you really wanna kick it up a notch it has seizures light setting. You can can change it to have just one color on. The drawers aren't very big but are deep so it holds quite a bit of clothes.My only problem with this dresser is that the materials were cheaper than what IKEA gives you. Little parts broke without much effort. They do give you spare parts like extra screws and whatnot. Still very cheap.In my video I showed how easy the wood splintered when securing the silver column/poles. Which is very upsetting due to it being the top of the dresser and it's pretty noticable. I wish the top part was a thicker wood to prevent that splintered area and it seems a little fragile; not sure it can hold a TV.Otherwise it's a very fun dresser just cheap materials.
